dcterms:creator: R. L. Peterson
dcterms:description: Thomson Reuters MarketPsych Indices (TRMI) measure the sentiment of market participants by distilling a massive collection of news and social media content through an extensive natural language processing framework. The indices consider different emotions (optimism, confusion, urgency etc.), as well as financial terms (interest rate, mergers etc.).
dcterms:title: Thomson Reuters MarketPsych Indices (TRMI)
